医 (F 醫)

[yī] (= 医学 yīxué) medical science;

    医生 yīshēng doctor;

    医院 yīyuàn hospital

土

[tǔ] earth, (= 土地 tǔdì) land, (= 土壤 tǔrǎng) soil

{Compare with 士 shì scholar}

罗 (F 羅)

[luó] (= 罗网 luówǎng) birdnet;

    罗马 Luómǎ Rome;

    罗盘 luópán compass

[luō] 罗嗦 luōsuo wordy, troublesome;

    哩哩罗罗 līliluōluō the sound of boiling/rumbling/etc.
